vative neighborhood
in Montreal, where women were expected to take on traditional roles and had=
 few ways of expressing themselves outside of their hairstyles and clothing=
=2E =E2=80=9CIt was terrifying to me=
,=E2=80=9D she told me. =E2=80=9CThat was=
 not what I thought life was all about.=E2=80=9D One painting, titled <em>A=
spirational</em> (2025), depicts a perfectly coiffed woman in a =E2=80=9Cch=
urch hat=E2=80=9D subtly patterned with blue eyes and eyelashes=E2=80=94her=
